nformwife(1555-1557)

Variable Type : computed

Description : Number of Former Wives (Computed in Flow Check E-1)

value label   Total
. INAPPLICABLE   3390
0 NONE   1097
1 1 FORMER WIFE   621
2 2 FORMER WIVES   81
3 3 FORMER WIVES   11
4 4 FORMER WIVES   3
998 Refused   2
999 Don't know   1
  Total   5206

Universe : Applicable if R has ever been married (fmarit = 1,2,3,4) and is not currently married for 1st time (numwife NE 1 and AD-7b MARSTAT NE 1)

nformcohab(1558-1560)

Variable Type : computed

Description : Number of Former Cohabiting Partners (Computed in Flow Check E-1)

value label   Total
. INAPPLICABLE   2150
0 NONE   1590
1 1 FORMER COHABITING PARTNER   778
2 2 FORMER COHABITING PARTNERS   396
3 3 FORMER COHABITING PARTNERS   146
4 4 FORMER COHABITING PARTNERS   66
5 5 OR MORE FORMER COHABITING PARTNERS   72
998 Refused   6
999 Don't know   2
  Total   5206

Universe : Applicable if R has ever cohabited and is not currently cohabiting for the 1st time (AB-1 MARSTAT NE 2 and numcohab GE 1)

Notes : This variable has been modified for public use, and the original variable is accessible by application to the NCHS Research Data Center. See Appendix 7 of the User's Guide for further information.

value label   Total
. INAPPLICABLE   4884
1 Yes   86
5 No   235
8 Refused   1
  Total   5206

Universe : Applicable if R reported no former wives as a recent sexual partner in section D (fwver = 1)
